================================================================================
! jQuery-powered update notification should only be shown on Joomla! 3 (throws an exception on Joomla! 2.5)
~ Warn users if they are using Joomla! 2.5.14 or earlier
# [HIGH] Upgrading from 2.x to 3.x could result in a broken site because the post-installation script couldn't run in some cases (also a problem in com_joomlaupdate - big whoops!)
# [MEDIUM] The CLI update script doesn't work under Joomla! 2.5
# [LOW] The Options page had untranslated strings under Joomla! 2.5
# [LOW] Wrong icon colors in optional version installation buttons

